			Profile
			
			GuoxiangPengisQiuShiDistinguishedProfessorofChinesePhilosophy,IntellectualHistoryandReligiousStudiesatZhejiangUniversity,andDirectoroftheCenterforCulturalChinaStudies,InstituteforAdvancedHumanisticStudiesatPekingUniversity.HewastheArthurLynnDistinguishedAndrewsChairvisitingprofessoratUniversityofHawai’i,visitingprofessorattheChineseUniversityofHongKong,visitingscholaratHarvardUniversity,visitingresearchfellowatNationalTaiwanUniversityandtheMaxPlanckInstitutefortheStudyofReligiousandEthnicDiversity,HumboldtFellowatRuhr-UniversityBochumandDistinguishedVisitingScholaratNationalUniversityofSingapore.Heservesasthevice-presidentoftheInternationalSocietyforComparativeStudiesofChineseandWesternPhilosophy,vice-presidentofChineseSocietyfortheLearningofWangYangming,andadvisoryboardmemberofEuropeanJournalforPhilosophyofReligion,CenterforEastAsianandComparativePhilosophyatCityUniversityofHongKong,editorialboardmemberofComparativeandContinentalPhilosophy,ComparativeandContinentalPhilosophyBookSeries,StudiesinChineseReligions,FrontiersofPhilosophyinChina,andmemberoftheCounciloftheInternationalConfucianAssociation.HereceivedvariousawardsandfellowshipsincludingFriedrichWilhelmBesselResearchAwardfromtheHumboldtFoundationandMinistryofEducationandResearchofGermany.HispublicationsincludeTheUnfoldingoftheLearningoftheInnateGoodness:WangLongxiandWangYangming’sTeachinginthemid-lateMing(Taipei:StudentBookCompany,2003;Beijing:SanlianBookStore,2005),ConfucianTradition:BetweenReligionandHumanism(Beijing:PekingUniversityPress,2007),ConfucianTraditionandChinesePhilosophy:ProspectandRetrospectinaNewCentury(Shijiazhuang:HebeiRenminPress,2009),ConfucianTraditionfromClassicalPeriodtoItsContemporaryTransformation:SpeculationandInterpretation(Wuhan:WuhanUniversityPress,2012),RevisionandNewDiscovery:HistoricalStudyofPre-ModernConfucianism(Taipei:AsianCulturePress,2013;Beijing,Zhonhuashuju,2015),ReconstructionofThisCultureofOurs:ConfucianismandModernWorld(Beijing:PekingUniversityPress,2013)andnumerousarticles.
			
				
